description: Number of n-node rooted unlabeled trees with out-degree <=2 and exactly 2 edges at the root.
references: S. J. Cyvin et al., Enumeration of constitutional isomers of polyenes, J. Molec. Structure (Theochem), 357 (1995), 255-261.
links: Index entries for sequences related to rooted trees
formula: G.f. satisfies A(x) = (W(x)-x)*(1-x)/x-x, where W(x) is g.f. for A001190.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
